{"tid":1686481,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"區選大戰略 20點——我地唔係冇野做！！","createTime":"2019-11-01T06:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T11:03:18.000Z","uid":251766,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c9fc5aedc4bebb881249499f6de8e2587e856f43","tid":1686481,"uid":251766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:57:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">區選我們一定要贏！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins><strong>整體篇</strong></ins></span></span>&mdash;&mdash;點解區選咁重要? <br />\n<br />\n1. 區選好緊要。區選好緊要。區選好緊要。<br />\n<br />\n2. 200萬人，每一個人都要努力為區選做些事情，什麼都可以，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目標是：贏得一區就一區，最好是五五。</span></span><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">攻下一區，好過你去裝修議辦處更有實質用處。</span></strong>現有的政治現實，你只能用盡全力去玩區選，對家非常害怕。<br />\n<br />\n3. <strong>區選勝利好處一</strong>：拿下更多<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特首選委</span></span></strong></strong>和<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>立法會超區</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n4. <strong>區選勝利好處二</strong>：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>培養社區民主新血</strong></span></span>。還記得沙燕橋之戰嗎？<br />\n<br />\n5. <strong>區選勝利好處三</strong>：支援各區開花，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>監督暴力</strong></span></span>，<strong>區議員係可以救人</strong>！<br />\n<br />\n6. <strong>區選勝利好處四</strong>：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">搶更多資源</span></span></strong>，吸納更多<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">基層街坊</span></span></strong>，敵做我要做！<br />\n<br />\n7. <strong>區選勝利好處五</strong>：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攔截智能燈柱</span></span></strong>和社區<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大白象</span></span></strong>工程。<br />\n<br />\n8. 每一區<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只能有一個泛民候選人，多一個則一定輸！</span></span></strong>多的話請街坊<strong>自行組織初選，不願意初選的可以全民抵制</strong>。不好意思，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大局為重，還是你個人夢想為重？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><ins>助選篇</ins></span></strong>&mdash;&mdash;除左投票有咩可以做？<br />\n<br />\n9. 200萬人，全民準備助選。感激很多<strong>素人落區</strong>參選，<strong><ins>成本極高，但水平參差不齊</ins></strong>，<strong>有的文宣很難看，有的幾乎沒有助選團</strong>，要贏，就一定要有人助選。一個人參選，起碼還有幕僚、文膽、出設、金主，還有要很多很多的<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">街頭助選團</span></span></strong>。只有200萬人一起助選，我們才有贏的機會。<br />\n<br />\n10. 年輕仔女，幫忙街站助選，親切的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">派單張給街坊</span></span></strong>。但切記不要落單，免得被斬。<br />\n<br />\n11. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">銀髮族</span></span></strong>，好緊要，因為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">很多區的高齡選民是被種票，最能改變他們的就是同是銀髮族</span></span></strong>，能有一票變節就離勝利多一小步。<br />\n<br />\n12. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中產朋友</span></span></strong>幫手做金主課金。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">很多素人，尤其是年輕人</span></span></strong>，連買gear也沒錢，何況是大量文宣？<br />\n<br />\n13. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">設計人，廣告人</span></span></strong>！大量需要！一個好的出設是勝選的必要條件！但<strong>很多素人不懂宣傳，不懂包裝自己</strong>，浪費了參選的機會...<br />\n<br />\n14. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民敬老日</span></span></strong>。為了防止老人院長輩被姑娘收身分證，被投票，請大家當日早上一早去接老飲茶。投給誰或怎樣投讓老人家自己決定，關鍵跟他們說明香港過去半年來發生什麼事。<br />\n<br />\n15. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">游擊隊</span></span></strong>。<strong>去每個建制的票站去拷問他們的良心</strong>，如果還有：你支持五大訴求嗎？你怎麼看一個個年輕人被打到全身是血？不然就帶著pad和speaker，在他們街站前不斷播放那些建制議員怎麼發言。<br />\n<br />\n16. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區連儂牆</span></strong></span>，貼上各<strong>建制派議員說過的話</strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提醒全香港人，這些人怎麼出賣香港</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n17. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">語言偽術師</span></span></strong>：當日投完票，看到凡是香港研究協會、香港社會監察及香港社區研究中心，必須<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>自然地走上前被他們捕獲，然後口投建制派，這樣可破壞它們的配票機器。</strong></span></span>投完票，遊走各票站門口繼續玩。也要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><ins>教懂銀髮族玩，因為他們對年輕人比較警惕</ins></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><ins>選區篇</ins></strong></span>&mdash;&mdash;人越多越安全<br />\n<br />\n18. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>紅色警戒</strong></span></span>：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>觀塘</strong></span>區，赤紅，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">智能燈柱先行區</span></strong>。需要多點手足幫忙助選，<strong>保護參選人</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n19. <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>紅色警戒</strong></span>：荃灣、屯門，何妖地頭。北區、離島、元朗、大埔，傳統鄉事地頭。東區，福建人地頭。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>需要多點助選團保護參選人，完全不夠人！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n20. <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黃色警戒</span></span>：西貢、沙田，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大量撞區</strong></span>，請民主大黨自行先<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">協調初選</span></strong>，否則請手足組織初選，不願參與就可以視為非同路人，只支持願意初選的候選人。<br />\n<br />\n最後，沒有最後：拋磚引玉，大家一起brainstorming，思考更多的戰術。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我們一定要贏！</span></strong></span><del><del></del></del>"},{"pid":"6e495757b21585eb3330d67897ced676e7feea45","tid":1686481,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T06:59:55.000Z","msg":"【突發】11月2活動需要大量文宣，你我都做到<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/erxDBS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/erxDBS</a>"},{"pid":"5ac2b9d5051b3be585aee3257813fc1ecd3c1bfe","tid":1686481,"uid":303932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:00:36.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"ac68970dd1873247e1ef0c27fb263c6eebd22696","tid":1686481,"uid":251766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:03:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />p 牌推唔郁"},{"pid":"4a9fbcb42efd7b338d67f36dd391d373976c11c8","tid":1686481,"uid":275006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"5af5220508356b77a2312e6a5dcbe0e54f8b882d","tid":1686481,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"ed3d0b7912bc0b369371faa81a76feaf5553539d","tid":1686481,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:12:16.000Z","msg":"曱近平"},{"pid":"9163ddae428c29e4f59761c03d74d60d0c8e1ad5","tid":1686481,"uid":251766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:13:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0b276acd5955babfdbf57a6f09b4c72df468284","tid":1686481,"uid":251766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"d7fc999db776069b890968e7ab84bd978d1e7b49","tid":1686481,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:21:55.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"3deec6c3c3fbb26fa02b6f7faafa4cdf6b32bf54","tid":1686481,"uid":321374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"攪對方辦事處只會為對家助選"},{"pid":"411779a3fa8458380ab53fe2192ea5703d8149c3","tid":1686481,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"甴敗敗"},{"pid":"1911782e932565a3ad30cade9c669999aa768556","tid":1686481,"uid":67172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"甴失腳"},{"pid":"293a4e2b499b43d53aa5a4d683a04cb6ad91b20f","tid":1686481,"uid":201575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"